        {
            "title": "A股午後升幅擴大  深股收升逾2%  兩市成交逾23400億人幣",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A股午後升破上午高位，深股升幅擴大至超過2%，創業板指數收升逾3%，兩市成交合計23416.78億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-15.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-15.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">上證綜指全日報4055，升28點或0.7%，今早以4030點開市，升2點或0.07%，早段見4028點，升1點，為全日低位，三頭馬車數據公布，大市向上，午後升破上午低位，見4057，升30點或0.74%，為全日高位。全日成交 9765.65億元</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">深證成指全日報14796，升297點或2.05%，今早開市報14546點，亦升47點或0.33%。早段見14522，跌24點或0.17%，為全日低位，午後高見14807，升309點或2.13%，為全日高位，半日成交13651.13億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬深300指數收報4736，升51點或1.1%，今早開升9點或0.2%，開報4694點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">創業板指數全日報3626點，升111點或3.17%，今早開市報3531點，升16點或0.46%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15880579-a%e8%82%a1%e5%8d%88%e5%be%8c%e5%8d%87%e5%b9%85%e6%93%b4%e5%a4%a7-%e6%b7%b1%e8%82%a1%e6%94%b6%e5%8d%87%e9%80%be2-%e5%85%a9%e5%b8%82%e6%88%90%e4%ba%a4%e9%80%be23400%e5%84%84%e4%ba%ba%e5%b9%a3",
